<item>
            <title>[LU-16590] Initialize ra_cur_pages</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16590</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &apos;ra_cur_pages&apos; atomic, used to track currently used pages in readahead, is not initialized.&#160; This means it will occasionally contain some unexpected value rather than 0, which can break readahead.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Initialize it to 0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
